接口 WorkStationListener

  • 所有超级接口:
    NotifierListener<SimComponent,java.lang.Object>, SimComponentLifeCycleListener
    所有已知实现类:
    MachineStatCollector

    public interface WorkStationListener
extends SimComponentLifeCycleListener
    Possible base class for workstation listeners. Delegates all events to seperate methods. Additional events can be processed by overriding SimComponentLifeCycleListener.handleOther(SimComponent, Object).
    作者:
    Torsten Hildebrandt
